data.description: This "GEM" has been REDUCED by 15k....a must have...lovely corner lot home  with impressive features. The soaring vaulted ceilings of over 20 feet, and a massive family room with a stone fireplace. Texas size gourmet kitchen with huge island and plenty of cabinet space. Oversized master suite with a modern spa like master bath and plenty of closet space. Living room and kitchen features high windows that overlook an extended covered patio. The house has some amazing features..... built in beer/wine chiller, landscape lighting, overhead garage storage system and a Home Theater Room (in wall Dolby Atmos 7.1 sound speaker system and sound wall insulation).
